    "The livestream is currently not running. Check the schedule to see when the next event takes place." : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Der Livestream ist momentan nicht aktiv. Sieh im Spielplan nach, wann die nächste Veranstaltung stattfindet."
          }
        },
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "The livestream is currently not running. Check the schedule to see when the next event takes place."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "The moers festival app helps you to easily find your way around the program. You can also put together your own program in the app and get lots of other important information." : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Die moers festival App hilft Dir, Dich im Programm zurecht zu finden. Du kannst Dir außerdem in der App Dein eigenes Programm zusammenstellen und viele weitere wichtige Informationen bekommen."
          }
        },
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "The moers festival app helps you to easily find your way around the program. You can also put together your own program in the app and get lots of other important information."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "This app has been developed and maintained by Lennart Fischer since 2018. What started out as a purely volunteer project has now become an essential part of the festival. If you have any ideas for new features, please feel free to send me your feedback. I’d also appreciate a (positive) review in the App Store." : {
      "comment" : "A description of the app's development and the user's feedback.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated" : true,
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Diese App wird seit 2018 von Lennart Fischer entwickelt und gepflegt. Anfangs noch reines Volunteer-Projekt, ist sie nun zu einem essentiellen Bestandteil des Festivals geworden. Falls Du Ideen für neue Funktionen hast, dann schreib mir gerne ein Feedback. Außerdem freue ich mich über eine (gute) Bewertung im App Store."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "This app is a project by the Code for Niederrhein group and was developed by Lennart Fischer.\n\n\nAll data is provided without guarantee." : {
      "comment" : "Text describing the disclaimer for the app.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated" : true
    },
    "This app is a project by the Code for Niederrhein group and was developed by Lennart Fischer.\\n\\n\\nAll data is provided without guarantee." : {
      "extractionState" : "manual",
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Diese App ist ein Projekt der Gruppe CodeForNiederrhein und wurde von Lennart Fischer entwickelt.\\n\\n\\nAlle Angaben zu Daten sind ohne Gewähr."
          }
        },
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "This app is a project by the Code for Niederrhein group and was developed by Lennart Fischer.\\n\\n\\nAll data is provided without guarantee."
          }
        }
      }
    },
